article_title: ‘More Than a Simple Riot’: Florida Man Will Spend Eight Months Behind Bars in First Felony Sentencing for the U.S. Capitol Breach
meta_description: Captured on surveillance video waving a Donald Trump flag near the dais of the U.S. Senate Chamber on Jan. 6th, Florida man Paul Hodgkins received an 8-month prison term on Monday.
